      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. WILL (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at Warragul in a handy 22.55 beating Blessed Rain. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. One of the key runners again. MASTER MCGRAW (4) was in the money last time at this track (29.74) in a Special conditions H, finishing a 2 length third. Has already won out of this draw. Suited here and expected to run well. ELUSIVE CURL (6) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 515m behind Secret Bandit (30.28) in a Special conditions H. Was in the money prior to that. Cannot be underestimated. ULENTA BALE (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
